# Skills Navigation

When a task matches a playbook, consult the corresponding folder in `.ai/skills/`:

- Full CRUD resource scaffold: `.ai/skills/admin-domain-page/`
- ky API objects: `.ai/skills/creating-api-clients/`
- Route pages (dashboard, reports, login): `.ai/skills/creating-route-pages/`
- Domain forms + zod/rhf: `.ai/skills/creating-domain-forms/`
- Domain view components: `.ai/skills/creating-domain-views/`

Cursor rule shortcuts: `/admin-domain-page`, `/creating-api-clients`, `/creating-route-pages`, `/creating-domain-forms`, `/creating-domain-views`
